name: SolChicks
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.

description.en: Our mission is to be the leading fantasy NFT PvP and P2E gaming ecosystem on the Solana blockchain. We built our game around adorable SolChick NFT collectibles, where players use their SolChicks as their characters in a unique gaming metaverse.
